{"tid":952144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先同我大佬叫雞","createTime":"2018-12-23T01:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T02:17:16.000Z","uid":83097,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"20765dc2483e00f962850bc4f6c3f963e8c3f7af","tid":952144,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:13:58.000Z","msg":"今日同我大佬去叫雞 係開心仔既<br />\n我大佬話成個雞場係佢睇撚晒<br />\n啲雞免費任屌唔嬲 堅係正既<br />\n<br />\n一齊叫完雞 開心完之後<br />\n佢就同我講話<br />\n我好做得野 而且係跟得佢最耐既o靚<br />\n所以決定遲下俾呢個雞場我睇<br />\n<br />\n爽 有雞場睇 今晚屌閪我既!!!"},{"pid":"1076097c5ebe6fb776dbe917986ec9301c51562e","tid":952144,"uid":213441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:41:10.000Z","msg":"pathetic <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca56d6b16bb3d1a8148e74554a35dbb2bea31530","tid":952144,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:52:10.000Z","msg":"好👌"},{"pid":"f1480b486b55401dbdb22246b05fef09060dc092","tid":952144,"uid":77092,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:53:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa70e6cd6b7c1ae0dc5513efa8d295db0de13e2a","tid":952144,"uid":122570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:54:11.000Z","msg":"岩岩出院？"},{"pid":"4bb0f0d82ae91960db668ad39b81ca7283027c96","tid":952144,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1076097c5ebe6fb776dbe917986ec9301c51562e","tid":952144,"uid":213441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:41:10.000Z","msg":"pathetic <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"入我個雞場我請你叫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb7da4c1c5ccac6eb23fdf8c6ed4fc95b5411af","tid":952144,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa70e6cd6b7c1ae0dc5513efa8d295db0de13e2a","tid":952144,"uid":122570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB